title: Bobby’s Top 5 Nicest Country Artists + Dr. Unger On Raymundo’s ‘Brotox’ + Lunchbox Tries To Pull A Shaq Move!
itunes:title: Bobby’s Top 5 Nicest Country Artists + Dr. Unger On Raymundo’s ‘Brotox’ + Lunchbox Tries To Pull A Shaq Move!
description:
Bobby ranks his Top 5 nicest country artists of all-time. We talk to Dr. Unger (Board Certified Plastic Surgeon) about performing Raymundo’s “Brotox” and helping Bae get cancer free post breast cancer. Lunchbox was so upset at the story about Shaq that made the news…he decided to try and pull a similar stunt.
